data.description: Rare gem! This single-level 3-bedroom ranch sits proudly on a sprawling .84-acre lot, boasting a large workshop and RV/boat shed. Free from HOA constraints, revel in the freedom of your fenced backyard retreat. The master bedroom invites with its expansive walk-in closet, while the large kitchen with solid surface countertops, a spacious pantry, and a convenient laundry room nearby. Park with ease in the oversize two-car garage and unwind on the charming covered deck. Covered Boat or vehicle Parking off the back of the workshop.  City water plus a well for irrigation! A Must See Home!
